{"tid":2207894,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★突發】PS5炒價已逾萬元！有人訂購後即炒賣","createTime":"2020-09-18T12:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T13:48:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce5a88557a30f9d33d908fe19d8b91803b3e5cb","tid":2207894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"Sony PlayStation 5（下稱 PS5）雖然要等到 11 月 19 日才在香港開售，但由今日（9 月 18 日）起已在世界各地市場開訂，香港各個可預訂的零售點，都有人龍排隊，而接受網上預訂的網站，則早於正式開放前已經「死機」，中午後多個網上交易平台隨即有人放售PS5，叫價上萬元，氣氛有如多年前炒賣新iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訂完即放訂單、PS5 炒單都炒過＄10,000<br />\n<br />\n有炒家眼見現在市場反應熾熱，不等實機推出，直接就把訂單放上網進行炒賣，索價＄7,000至＄10,000 港幣不等，雖然不知有否買家「接貨」，但據記者觀察，這類型的炒家數量不少，單是在拍賣平台 Carousell 上已有十數單據放售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/525237/ps5%E7%82%92%E5%83%B9%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E5%B8%82%E7%8F%BE%E4%BA%BA%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%88%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%AD%BB%E6%A9%9F-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A8%82%E8%B3%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E7%82%92%E8%B3%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F525237%2Fps5%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%2580%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B8%2582%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25BE%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%2588%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A8%2582%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258D%25B3%25E7%2582%2592%25E8%25B3%25A3&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=1b46b2f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/525237/ps5%E7%82%92%E5%83%B9%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A%E9%96%80%E5%B8%82%E7%8F%BE%E4%BA%BA%E9%BE%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%88%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99%E6%AD%BB%E6%A9%9F-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%A8%82%E8%B3%BC%E5%BE%8C%E5%8D%B3%E7%82%92%E8%B3%